Title: Line Up or Shut Up
Plot: When a young man is found dead in an expensive sports car he was delivering to a diplomat, each clue leads Carrie and Al to yet another possible motive for the murder.
GuestStars: Makenzie Leigh, Dennis Christopher, Vito D'Ambrosio, Olivia Birkelund, Ben Becher, Ilene Kristen, Dale Soules, Angel L. Caban, Juan Castano, Peter Allas, Tommy Walker, Jonathan Hova, Candice Bryant
